      "rationale": "Scoped out at MRL 2. The k-omega SST turbulence model and power-law hemolysis damage accumulation model are selected based on literature consensus for blood pump CFD; formal model-form uncertainty quantification is not required at this risk level."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
